text.tspan: A sweet yellow beer with fruity hops, Elderflower and
Every year those white flowers taunt us to pick them,
but only to have gone with the wind when one finally
leaves the coach. Ha! Not this year!
You go ahead now - smell those delicate aromas -
giving them flowers a lovely purpose ... Cheers!
